  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a Phase II trial assessing the safety and preliminary efficacy of daily APL-2
      subcutaneous infusion administered for 16 weeks with a 6 month safety follow up, in patients
      with glomerulopathies
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
